text: Rikutoshi Maeda (born 17 February 1931) is a Japanese equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
